Package Name: The LDPL Socket Library
Short Name: ldpl_socket
Author: dvkt
Version: 1.0.0
Website: https://github.com/dvkt/ldpl-socket
Info: The LDPL Socket Library allows you to open, close, write to,
and read from network sockets in LDPL. It's mostly made for clients -
if you want to write a server, please see the LDPL Network Server
Library at https://www.github.com/lartu/ldpl-net-server. Requires
LDPL 4.3 or greater.
